Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:51.76,黄昏-JN_内,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H000000&\fs55\pos(680,480)}不哭嘛
